trans-unit.source: Provides basic functionality for describing the structure of a data source at design time.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder grunnleggende funksjonalitet for som beskriver strukturen til en datakilde ved utformingen.

trans-unit.source: Implement the IDataSourceSchema interface to describe a custom data source at design time.
trans-unit.target: Implementere grensesnittet IDataSourceSchema for Ã¥ beskrive en egendefinert datakilde under utformingen.

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DataSetSchema>, <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.XmlDocumentSchema>, and <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TypeSchema> classes implement the IDataSourceSchema interface.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DataSetSchema>, <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.XmlDocumentSchema>, og <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TypeSchema>klasser implementere grensesnittet IDataSourceSchema.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TypeSchema> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.XmlDocumentSchema> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DataSetSchema>

trans-unit.source: Classes that implement the IDataSourceSchema are used by custom control designer components to provide lists of fields and views for data-bound controls at design time.
trans-unit.target: Klasser som implementerer IDataSourceSchema som brukes av egendefinert kontroll designer komponenter oppgi lister med felt og visninger for databundet Kontroller under utformingen.

trans-unit.source: Gets an array of schema descriptors for views contained in the data source.
trans-unit.target: Henter en matrise av skjemaet beskrivelser for visninger i datakilden.

trans-unit.source: A class that implements the GetViews method returns an array of objects that implement the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IDataSourceViewSchema> interface.
trans-unit.target: En klasse som implementerer metoden GetViews returnerer en matrise av objekter som implementerer den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IDataSourceViewSchema>grensesnittet.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IDataSourceViewSchema>

trans-unit.source: For example, in the array returned by the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DataSetSchema.GetViews%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method, each element of the array is a <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DataSetViewSchema> object that implements <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IDataSourceViewSchema>.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel i matrisen som returneres av <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DataSetSchema.GetViews%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden, hvert element i matrisen er et <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DataSetViewSchema>objekt som implementerer <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IDataSourceViewSchema>.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IDataSourceViewSchema> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DataSetViewSchema> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DataSetSchema.GetViews%2A?displayProperty=fullName>
